BFD-MGMT-SESSION-DETAIL:

BFD Detailed Session Information

mp-download-state: BFD-MGMT-MP-DOWNLOAD-STATE-INFO

MP Dowload State

Association session information

BFD-MGMT-SESSION-ASSOCIATION-INFORMATION
status-information: BFD-MGMT-SESSION-STATUS-INFORMATION

Session status information

lsp-ping-info: BFD-MGMT-LSP-PING-INFO

LSP Ping Info

owner-information: BFD-MGMT-SESSION-OWNER-INFORMATION

Client applications owning the session
